OL,3,C'Heartbroken' Mariah Carey confirms
OL,4,Cher mother and sister died on same day
OL,6,FMariah Carey has confirmed her mother,
OL,7,FPatricia, and sister, Alison, have
OL,8,Fboth died on the same day.
OL,10,F"My heart is broken that I've lost my
OL,11,Fmother this past weekend," the pop
OL,12,Fsuperstar said in a statement.
OL,14,F"Sadly, in a tragic turn of events, my
OL,15,Fsister lost her life on the same day.
OL,16,FI feel blessed that I was able to
OL,17,Fspend the last week with my mom before
OL,18,Fshe passed.
